oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同路呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過我都仲plan緊行程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身都想去西藏同蒙古呀<br />\n不過有個fd氣管唔好 佢話唔想去呢啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw之前去過北京內蒙 真係好正<br />\n但唔敢自己去埋俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa62420394075d98c8318479290e5e090da6eeb","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係絲就千其千其唔好去印度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好想去印度呀<br />\n不過男朋友應該唔會比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318d36acd9991e0e525a75b115e94cef9ea95ef0","tid":213773,"uid":4570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"絲打我都係今年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我grad trip 就去越南 西藏同伊朗<br />\n伊朗就自己毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波斯真係我25歲之前想去既地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8554ecf0bdd3d900ceb4322d42366145af3a9f91","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打我都係今年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我grad trip 就去越南 西藏同伊朗<br />\n伊朗就自己毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波斯真係我25歲之前想去既地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你巴定絲<br />\n<br />\n毒遊真係好想試一次<br />\n但我好撚細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果呢世有機會毒遊 應該都係遊印度<br />\n一不做 二不休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b82209ee2bab0926390b6f6c832a19ad04ea9b","tid":213773,"uid":13835,"like":0,"disli