=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：上個sem break去咗 好正</blockquote><br />\n嗚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到好想去<br />\n介唔介意講用咗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西伯利亞應該係我返工之後請年假去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同俄羅斯一併去埋<br />\n不過俄羅斯仲想去埋海參威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c32ebe1483e0ce200df1e66c67637802635a3fe","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想去港女勝地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲們有咩好地方同行程推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去東歐</blockquote><br />\n歐洲其實算唔算亂<br />\n我應該都係2-3個女仔去<br />\n<br />\n成日聽人講好易比人搶野"},{"pid":"583034698c34a0ea88094be4047bbf4eb8cce853","tid":213773,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"有錢有計傾"},{"pid":"cf40e5bea0047f0f8119cc0fe4f2ced89ab3eee1","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西伯利亞鐵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：上個sem break去咗 好正</blockquote><br />\n嗚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到好想去<br />\n介唔介意講用咗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大約萬5 三星期<br />\nbackpacker 住青年旅舍</blockquote><br />\n你住男女一齊訓嗰啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126e570fd2b7ef9a7a5abc36af3c6a1251b94574","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢有計傾</blockquote><br />\n我唔洗豪玩豪食<br />\n主要想睇靚景 同平時接觸唔到既人吹下水咁<br />\n<br />\n利申 英文麻麻"},{"pid":"2a5ed834ea2f590fde0edb64aee9a69e297f341f","tid":213773,"uid":4570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打我都係今年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我grad trip 就去越南 西藏同伊朗<br />\n伊朗就自己毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波斯真係我25歲之前想去既地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你巴定絲<br />\n<br />\n毒遊真係好想試一次<br />\n但我好撚細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果呢世有機會毒遊 應該都係遊印度<br />\n一不做 二不休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以係台灣試下毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小試牛刀<br />\n但係去d體驗地方毒遊先有feel <br />\n唔係好鐘意成日買野<br />\n之後year 2去歐洲毒遊係慕尼黑個British garden 到可以攤左成日 涼涼地又舒服又有景色好靚</blockquote><br />\n我都想做男人 毒遊都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想去體驗多過shopping <br />\n<br />\n台南好似有啲藝術村 都想去<br />\n但自己一個 真係去邊都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇圖share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/205228_cfc7abdc726712ca25099bc94b503369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F205228_cfc7abdc726712ca25099bc94b503369.jpg&h=865efd67&s={SIZE}\" />有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我上次去左都幾多地方 好似波蘭既Wroclaw, Poznan, Krakow, Gdansk, Warsaw 仲有Prague, CK, Berlin, Munich, Vienna, Salzburg, Budapest <br />\n最鐘意都係Gdansk, Munich 同 Salzburg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係Salzburg book 唔切hostel 之後訓車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一個好好既體驗黎 每去到一個新既地方就會同同房既Backpacker 傾計去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/205228_16b48b07e69b65cb00580739554bfadb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F205228_16b48b07e69b65cb00580739554bfadb.jpg&h=a6105457&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/355D5e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F355D5e0.jpg&h=6fa77e18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9pK891.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9pK891.jpg&h=6b692bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjHwR02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjHwR02.jpg&h=5d0178a4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 真係始終巴同絲既考慮點都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住車站好似幾正<br />\n我之前去Nepal有機會住到local屋但一晚<br />\n都真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同平時旅行唔同玩法<br />\n<br />\n不過都係嗰句 巴絲有別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒遊就係今日唔知聽日事<br />\n不斷挑戰自己comfort zone <br />\n以前我係一個做咩都要plan 一輪既人，怕輸<br />\n依家變到咩都試左先既人<br />\n其實絲打除左怕男朋友唔比之外仲有咩原因令到你卻步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851bbec8a6d4992fbff8a903c82b9e89e6227885","tid":213773,"uid":4570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想去港女勝地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲們有咩好地方同行程推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去東歐</blockquote><br />\n歐洲其實算唔算亂<br />\n我應該都係2-3個女仔去<br />\n<br />\n成日聽人講好易比人搶野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算 其實有好多野整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84a5363e820d001f044e14a3ab31d29084ebfae","tid":213773,"uid":4570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢有計傾</blockquote><br />\n我去左兩個月歐洲都係洗萬五only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 靠自己補習儲錢+ 住coachsurfing<br />\nHostel 都有住"},{"pid":"b4db4bf410ee3bc9fa8a80ac5ec5775e54703d5a","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打我都係今年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我grad trip 就去越南 西藏同伊朗<br />\n伊朗就自己毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波斯真係我25歲之前想去既地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你巴定絲<br />\n<br />\n毒遊真係好想試一次<br />\n但我好撚細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果呢世有機會毒遊 應該都係遊印度<br />\n一不做 二不休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以係台灣試下毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小試牛刀<br />\n但係去d體驗地方毒遊先有feel <br />\n唔係好鐘意成日買野<br />\n之後year 2去歐洲毒遊係慕尼黑個British garden 到可以攤左成日 涼涼地又舒服又有景色好靚</blockquote><br />\n我都想做男人 毒遊都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想去體驗多過shopping <br />\n<br />\n台南好似有啲藝術村 都想去<br />\n但自己一個 真係去邊都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇圖share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji