normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒遊就係今日唔知聽日事<br />\n不斷挑戰自己comfort zone <br />\n以前我係一個做咩都要plan 一輪既人，怕輸<br />\n依家變到咩都試左先既人<br />\n其實絲打除左怕男朋友唔比之外仲有咩原因令到你卻步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕危險呀 始終女仔有咩事都係比較蝕<br />\n搶又唔夠人搶 惡又唔夠人惡<br />\n<br />\n不過最主要都係因為男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb4560039ff0eec3e36f7c4193200768ecdaa84","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想去港女勝地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲們有咩好地方同行程推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去東歐</blockquote><br />\n歐洲其實算唔算亂<br />\n我應該都係2-3個女仔去<br />\n<br />\n成日聽人講好易比人搶野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算 其實有好多野整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n我有朋友去15日 比人搶左3次野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要周圍都無人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2421edab4ac66e69ea3346f7dfd2bbbea58150aa","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有錢有計傾</blockquote><br />\n我去左兩個月歐洲都係洗萬五only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 靠自己補習儲錢+ 住coachsurfing<br />\nHostel 都有住</blockquote><br />\n咁真係抵玩喎<br />\n我以前大洗去台灣5、6日都萬幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n依家諗起覺得好蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6be940ea06ceb9ea0c659db597e2335b54c908","tid":213773,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"咁都負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8673020979c403af9ede2c4bfb812b2cac0ed40","tid":213773,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩上網搵左Hungary啲圖，好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/193653_ee7e966b971884b306ab8f2ba1f3858d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F193653_ee7e966b971884b306ab8f2ba1f3858d.jpg&h=4822fe15&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHungary係我暫時去過歐洲國家之中最鍾意嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想再去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去嗰時係住咩地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n住airbnb呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住一間好地道嘅apartment <br />\n嗰邊物價低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好平"},{"pid":"581ca5d7e23f428cdb1a841957e66bc4e4f1a498","tid":213773,"uid":93411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"印度"}]}